This book is also called Amalapuran, it talks about Pure devotional service unto the supreme Lord Krishna

It talks about the direct pastimes of Lord Krishna.

The author of this scripture is Vedavyas.Upon the instructions of Sage Naradamuni Vedavyas compiled this book. 

The conversation between Vedavyas and Naradamuni can be found in 1st canto 4,5,6 chapters. 